  "name": "RPlog_The_Great_Escape",
  "title": "The Great Escape",
  "summary": "Deep beneath the House of Sabacc casino on Nar Shaddaa, a New Republic marine team races to liberate slaves before they can be shipped out, tipped off by their Durosian contact Zalla that the sale has already gone through and half the captives are gone. Led by Siarra and the gruff Colonel Eckhart, with the pilot Tiaryn, the lethal Wroonian Kelnas, and the Quarren doctor Druze who slices the holding-area security network, the team silently kills the guards, cuts open the wire cages, and herds the malnourished, traumatized survivors toward a stolen shuttle ten levels down. The escape turns into a running firefight as guards emerge from the lift and slaver buyers' soldiers use prisoners as human shields, but the marines clear room after room with blades, blasters, and flashbang grenades. Pushing through the lawless lower levels to the landing pad, they fight free with forty of the original captives recovered, ten still missing, and load everyone aboard the waiting ships, with Druze's stolen manifests promising a chance to reclaim the lost.",
